message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this premium product at $12000. It’s a top-quality asset with exceptional value. Please let me know if you’re interested, and we can discuss further details.

Hi Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of your product, but I'm currently considering other options as well. I am able to offer $6000 for the product at this time. Please let me know if this is feasible for you.
